---
---
<section id="contacto" class="py-24 scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm border border-dali-dark/5 max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[0_30px_70px_rgba(61,52,46,0.04)]">
    <div class="text-center max-w-md mx-auto mb-10">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-dali-dark uppercase tracking-tight">¿Hacemos algo juntos?</h2>
      <p class="text-dali-dark/60 font-medium mt-2">Contame de tu proyecto, marca o idea. Me tomo un café y te respondo al toque. 🥐</p>
    </div>

    <form class="space-y-6 max-w-xl mx-auto" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-dali-dark/70 mb-2">Tu Nombre</label>
          <input type="text" placeholder="Dali" class="w-full bg-white/60 border border-dali-dark/10 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3.5 text-dali-dark placeholder:text-dali-dark/30 focus:outline-none focus:border-dali-toast font-medium transition-colors" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-dali-dark/70 mb-2">Tu Email</label>
          <input type="email" placeholder="dalila.dev.ar@gmail.com" class="w-full bg-white/60 border border-dali-dark/10 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3.5 text-dali-dark placeholder:text-dali-dark/30 focus:outline-none focus:border-dali-toast font-medium transition-colors" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-dali-dark/70 mb-2">Contame un poco más</label>
        <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Tengo una idea para mi marca..." class="w-full bg-white/60 border border-dali-dark/10 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3.5 text-dali-dark placeholder:text-dali-dark/30 focus:outline-none focus:border-dali-toast font-medium transition-colors resize-none"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-dali-dark text-white font-semibold text-base py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-dali-toast transition-colors duration-300 shadow-md shadow-dali-dark/5 cursor-pointer">
        Enviar Mensaje ✨
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>